    <title>参宿四星云的小站成功建站！</title>
    <url>/2023/01/21/3/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p><strong>参宿四星云的小站</strong>建站基本完成啦！在此要万分感谢<a class="link"   href="https://lalala123987.github.io/" >雷神同志 <i class="fa-regular fa-arrow-up-right-from-square fa-sm"></i></a>的耐心指导！</p>
